column2: SELECT top # s.ra, s.dec, s.z, g.d4#_sub, gSL.h_delta_eqw, gSI.v_disp, gSE.oh_p9#p5, gSL.h_alpha_flux, gSL.h_beta_flux, gSL.h_delta_flux, gSL.nii_#_flux, gSL.nii_#_flux, gSL.oiii_#_flux, gSL.oiii_#_flux, gSL.oiii_#_flux, gSL.oii_#_flux, gSL.oii_#_flux, gSL.oi_#_flux, gSL.sii_#_flux, s.CLASS FROM galSpecIndx as g  JOIN SpecObj AS s  ON g.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID JOIN galSpecLine as gSL  ON gSL.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID JOIN galSpecInfo as gSI  ON gSI.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID JOIN galSpecExtra as gSE  ON gSE.SpecobjID = s.SpecobjID WHERE (s.ra between # and #) and (s.dec between # and #) AND s.CLASS = &&&
